THE STATE PATTERN
The state pattern allows an object to behave differently when its state changes

COMPONENTS OF THE STATE PATTERN
-CONTEXT
 This class uses the current state for its utility
-STATE
    This is an abstract class with abstract methods that represents a current state(polymorphism).
-CONCRETESTATEA
    This class extends the state class and has a concrete implementation for the abstract methods
-CONCRETESTATEB
    This class also extends the state class and has a concrete implementation for the abstract methods.